CustomField.inlineHelpText: Mark this field true if you intended this DiagnosticNode screen to be the last screen that is presented to an end-user in a diagnostic pathway. If true, upon clicking "Next" on this screen, the next screen the end user will see is the "Finish" screen, with "Previous" and "Finish" buttons vs. "Previous" and "Next" buttons. Upon clicking "Finish" on that screen, the end-user will be routed back to the initial diagnostic start screen.
CustomField.label: End Node
